snippet.textDisplay:
Assalamualaikum.

Wow. Wow. Wow.
Just just amazing, fabulous, splendid, tremendous, significant, terrific. Like the dictionary is short of words for this piece of art. I wish I was part of this project.
The most beautiful thing watching and listening it is, that it has a very friendly, open, close to heart, casual feeling, yet appealing, where everybody relates him/herself to it. People from different cultures, so many languages put together, yet it does not feel alien. Feels like u r a part of it. It strikes your heart, your soul.

Amazing
